data.description: Take a walk through this impeccably maintained 4 bedroom, 3 full bathroom bungalow in Columbiana schools and fall in love. Located on a quiet street, just steps away from Firestone park. this spacious home is everything you have been searching for. On the main level you will find a beautiful kitchen with newer stainless appliances, multiple living spaces, two bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and as an added bonus, a fully enclosed 4 seasons room perfect for year round indoor/outdoor living. Upstairs you will find two additional bedrooms, another full bath and 3 flex rooms that could be utilized for a multitude of creative uses. Currently they are being showcased as individual libraries for the children.   With 14 closets throughout the home, a full basement and an abundance of kitchen cabinets, you will never lack for storage space. Whether you are just starting out, looking for some space to grow, busting at the seems in your current home, or looking for single floor living as you downsize, this could be the perfect next home for you. Recent updates include: roof (23), fridge (23), HWT (21) and newer windows. Call your favorite agent today to schedule a private tour.
